Given - I am logged in
And I am on the Page 8 of Cranial MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Cranial nerves' from the dropdown
And 'I describe' button is selected

When I select 'Differential diagnose' tab 

Then 'Differential diagnosis 1*' dropdown is enabled 
And '> 1 lesion of the same entity' checkbox is enabled 

When I select 'Acoustic neuroma' option from the 'Differential diagnosis 1*' dropdown 
Then 'Suspicion of' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Differential diagnosis 2' dropdown is enabled 

When I select 'Suspicion of' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected

When I select 'Schwannoma' option from 'Differential diagnosis 2' dropdown
Then 'Subordinate' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Differential diagnosis 3' dropdown is enabled 

When I select 'Subordinate' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected

When I select 'Penial cyst' from the 'Differential diagnosis 3' dropdown
Then option is selected 
